PrecisAppointment of MARIE LEGAULT as non-resident Consul General of Canada in Montserrat, as non-resident Consul General of Canada in Anguilla, and as non-resident Consul General of Canada in the British Virgin Islands, with residence in Bridgetown; and PETER MACARTHUR as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Timor-Leste, with residence in Jakarta.
